    nft

    My Pet Hooligan is a Web3 gaming ecosystem centered around a play-to-earn game featuring anthropomorphic rebel rabbits navigating a dystopian, satirical world controlled by an evil overlord corporation. It combines blockchain technology, NFTs, and immersive gameplay to empower players with ownership and creative participation in the game’s evolving story and economy.

    My Pet Hooligan NFT

    My Pet Hooligan (MPH) NFTs are 3D rabbit avatars that can be used in the game. MPH is centered around seven factions, each with unique characteristics, born from a rebellion against MetaZuckBot: Punk Bunnies, Mutants, Playboys, Rogue Jumpers, Cypher Buns, Bunners, and Hare Raisers. Holding an MPH NFT grants access to $KARRAT claims, future drops, and potential benefits like land ownership.

    Utility of the My Pet Hooligan NFT

    • Access to FBX Files: Enables 3D animation of your Hooligan in the Immi app.

    • Exclusive In-Game Goodies: Unlocks items and perks unavailable to non-holders, with more features planned.

    • Playable Character: Allows you to play as your Hooligan in future game versions.

    • Central Role in Ecosystem: Positions you for upcoming drops and activations, such as "The Others" and "Karrot Juice."

    • Enhanced In-Game Earnings: Provides benefits over free-to-play players in future updates.

    • Rental Opportunities: Potential to rent out your Hooligan to other players in the future.

    • Land Ownership: Future possibility to own land within the game.

    Retention

    ⚠️The retention method prioritizes two key aspects:

    1. Current Holding Cycle: It focuses first on the user’s ongoing holding period if they still possess the asset, ensuring active users are accurately represented.

    2. Longest Holding Period: For users with multiple buy-sell cycles, it captures only the longest holding period, reflecting their most significant engagement.

    This approach avoids double-counting and balances both current activity and meaningful long-term retention.

    Long Holding Times: Reflect strong belief in the project, suggesting that the owners see lasting value and utility beyond immediate profit.

    ⚠️ Note : The MPH ecosystem also includes other NFT's ( Zuckbots and zuck parts). They are currently not included in the analysis and is currently WIP. The do not posses any utility yet and hence are not a priority.
